to the combined Hiroshima and

01:57:47.480 --> 01:57:51.040
Nagasaki explosions. So that tells

01:57:51.120 --> 01:57:55.100
you if you wanted a megaton,
you need about 25 times

01:57:55.160 --> 01:57:58.660
more. So you would have to run
for 25 billion years to get a

01:57:58.700 --> 01:58:00.760
megaton of explosive power.

