01:59:32.820 --> 01:59:39.420
system if we can get to 0.2 times
the speed of light in 20 years.

01:59:40.560 --> 01:59:42.949
Meaning it would take us 20
years to get to Alpha Centauri.

01:59:43.800 --> 01:59:47.780
Is any of this a possible future,
the use of antimatter for

01:59:47.800 --> 01:59:51.320
generation of energy? Because we
should mention that it's extremely

01:59:51.420 --> 01:59:55.020
compact. It has the obvious
downsides that it's extremely

01:59:55.100 --> 01:59:58.900
