01:59:58.960 --> 02:00:00.980
The upside is it's compact.

02:00:01.000 --> 02:00:04.980
- It's very powerful. So the
short answer is it is not a

02:00:05.000 --> 02:00:08.480
physics problem, it's an engineering
problem. So I have people for that.

02:00:09.840 --> 02:00:09.940
- Well, yeah.

02:00:09.980 --> 02:00:14.940
- But no, no. The truth is that antimatter,

02:00:15.820 --> 02:00:19.680
if you are able to assemble
