02:00:19.820 --> 02:00:23.580
it would be able to take that
antimatter, heat up matter,

02:00:23.700 --> 02:00:26.700
and shoot it out the back
of a rocket, and it would,

02:00:27.740 --> 02:00:31.600
you know, do what rockets do, and it would
make us go quick, and that would be fine.

